autocmd FileType netrw setl bufhidden=wipe

" Hide highlight search after exit command-line
augroup vimrc-incsearch-highlight
    autocmd!
    autocmd CmdlineEnter /,\? :set hlsearch
    autocmd CmdlineLeave /,\? :set nohlsearch
augroup END

